Hosts. The main hosts of the adults are large and medium-sized domestic and wild ungulates: cattle, buffaloes, goats, camels, sheep, horses, chital, Axis axis (Erxleben), nilgai,
Boselaphus tragocamelus (Pallas)
, sambar,
Cervus unicolor Kerr
and an antelope. The adults have also been recorded from domestic dogs, tiger,
Panthera tigris (Linnaeus)
and humans (our data;
